    "body": "if you want less images to load, you can use `configure({ hitsPerPage: 5 })` to show only five hits, is that what you want? \r\n\r\nOtherwise if you're looking for lazy-loading, InstantSearch isn't opinionated around that, there's many solutions that exist for it that, even one builtin to the browser now (loading=lazy on the image) https://web.dev/browser-level-image-lazy-loading/",
